{"tid":1845120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[狠人] 陳肇始：靠湖北人自己申報","createTime":"2020-01-27T03:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T04:37:04.000Z","uid":19552,"like":16,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"65ee09b15e7c92f546d708cf95e3630c8c0933c2","tid":1845120,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T03:34:38.000Z","msg":"（超痴線！荒謬絕倫！）今朝聽香港電台《千禧年代》陳肇始局長講解關於防疫最新安排：<br />\n<br />\n主持人：點樣知道入境人士有冇去過湖北？<br />\n<br />\n陳肇：靠佢地自己申報<br />\n<br />\n主持人：點知佢講真話？<br />\n<br />\n陳肇：Er..... 我哋會度體溫，呢個係第一道防線<br />\n<br />\n主持人：如果佢發燒會點？<br />\n<br />\n陳肇：會送佢去香港嘅政府醫院隔離和接受治療<br />\n<br />\n.......<br />\n<br />\n主持人：現在見到高鐵係患者來港的主要途徑，點解張建宗上星期仲話高鐵唔需要健康申報？話驚係大堂有人群聚集？<br />\n<br />\n陳肇：我哋係收到前線人員（高鐵職員）的意見，佢地有呢個擔心；同埋申報都未必能作準....<br />\n<br />\n主持人：咁講法，咪自打嘴巴？去過湖北嘅人現在入境都一樣可以講大話？<br />\n<br />\n陳肇：Er.... <br />\n<br />\n（以上係真實對話，狠人精簡總結了....）<br />\n<br />\nRTHK：<a href=\"https://fbwat.ch/1xoehRNgqeFLXuVV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffbwat.ch%2F1xoehRNgqeFLXuVV&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420Rgp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=fa4b3e2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fbwat.ch/1xoehRNgqeFLXuVV</a>"},{"pid":"b5b5b13917cfafd99fada62e3db3b61e3fba3629","tid":1845120,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T03:36:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd61f8965f583a0f3bb7584764eb923b58566014","tid":1845120,"uid":17506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T03:36:49.000Z","msg":"用成千億就係為左收中共大禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffaa9503f5aa6f4857a7b0f1ea7030d8b5cddf62","tid":1845120,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T03:37:47.000Z","msg":"唔知收左幾多錢啦佢"},{"pid":"ffe47436242d5770dedfc2651423364fca8f73a6","tid":1845120,"uid":87396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T03:38:57.000Z","msg":"er........................ er佢老母啦 